# Scavenger Hunt Frontend - Environment Variables
# Copy to .env and adjust for your setup.

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Local development (default)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Leave VITE_API_URL unset or empty to use the Vite dev proxy (backend at localhost:8000).
# The proxy is configured in vite.config.ts: /api -> http://localhost:8000

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Production / deployed frontend pointing at Lambda
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Set to your API Gateway URL (no trailing slash) when the frontend is deployed
# separately (e.g. on Render) and needs to call the Lambda backend.
#
# Example:
# VITE_API_URL=https://idg6jtsow7.execute-api.us-east-1.amazonaws.com
